snippet.title: Meet Me In The Parking Lot - NES Gameplay trailer from Party Brains
snippet.description:
Coming soon to PartyBrains.com

Game made with NESMaker.  
Thank you to the NESMaker community for help with issues in coding.   

Special thanks to Dale Hollow for allowing me to use his song "I'm A Lover, but I'll Still Fight" off the legendary country EP, "IF YOU LOVE COUNTRY MUSIC".  

Ya hear that YouTube? I got permission. from the artist.  So lay off.
